snippet.title: On The Spot News Media
snippet.description: Jamaican news Jamaican foods Jamaican cuisine Jamaican culture Jamaican entertainment Jamaica. World News world events USA  Jamaican people Jamaican music Dancehall music music Jamaican language Jamaican Patois Jamaican rivers Jamaican beaches Jamaican hotels Jamaican resorts crime and violence in Jamaica. Jamaican reggae music and Jamaican track and field. This channel was created to show and give highlights of things happening in and around Jamaica and how what's going on affects Jamaica positively or negatively. This is a Jamaican channel with an international twist
